quran[6{c,v,t}:
2,191,"un se lrho jahan bhi tumhara unn se muqaabla paish aeye aur inhen nikalu jahan se unhon ne tum ko nikala hai, is liye ke qatal agarchay bura hai, magar fitnah is se bhi ziyada bura hai aur masjid haraam ke qareeb jab taq woh tum se nah lrhin, tum bhi nah lrho, magar jab woh wahan larnay se nah chukein, to tum bhi be takalouf inhen maro ke aisay kafiroon ki yahi saza hai"
2,192,"phir agar woh baz aa jayen, to jaan lau ke Allah maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
2,193,"tum un se lartay raho yahan taq ke fitnah baqi nah rahay aur deen Allah ke liye ho jaye phir agar woh baz aa jayen, to samajh lau ke zaalmon ke siwa aur kisi par dast Darazi rawa nahi"
2,194,"mah haraam ka badla haraam hi hai aur tamam hurmatoon ka lehaaz baRabari ke sath hoga lehazajo tumpar dast Darazi kere, tum bhi isi terhan is par dast Darazi karo Albata Allah se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke Allah inhen logon ke sath hai, jo is ki hudood tornay se parhaiz karte hain"
2,195,Allah ki raah mein kharch karo aur apne hathon apne aap ko halakat mein nah daalo ahsaan ka tareeqa ikhtiyar karo ke Allah mohsan-ooko pasand karta hai
2,196,"Allah ki khushnodi ke liye jab hajj aur omre ki niyat karo, to ussay poora karo aur agar kahin ghar jao to jo qurbani muyassar aeye, Allah ki janab mein paish karo aur apne sir nah mun-doojab taq ke qurbani apni jagah nah poanch jaye magar jo shakhs mareez ho ya jis ke sir mein koi takleef ho aur is bana par apna sir mundwa le, to ussay chahiye keh fiyayke tor par rozay rakhay ya sadqa day ya qurbani kere phir agar tumhe aman naseeb ho jaye ( aur tum hajj se pehlay mukkay poanch jao ), to jo shakhs tum mein se hajj ka zamana anay taq omre ka faida uthaye, woh hasb Maqdoor qurbani day, aur a gir qurbani muyassar nah ho, to teen rozay hajj ke zamane mein aur saat ghar poanch kar, iss terhan poooray das rozay rakh le yeh riayat unn logon ke liye hai, jin ke ghar baar masjid haraam ke qareeb nah hon Allah ke inn ehkaam ki khilaaf warzi se bachcho aur khoob jaan lau ke Allah sakht saza dainay wala hai"
